# Full System Architecture — Multi-Tenant Platform

## System Overview

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Frontend — Next.js Dashboard"
        FE_ONBOARD[Onboarding Wizard]
        FE_DASH[Tenant Dashboard]
        FE_MOD[Module Pages x62]
        FE_PLATFORM[Platform Admin]
    end

    subgraph "API Layer — Laravel"
        MW[Middleware Stack]
        CTRL[29 API Controllers]
        SVC[23 Services]
    end

    subgraph "Module System — 40 Modules"
        MOD_CORE["Core: Ecommerce, POS, CRM, Finance, Inventory, HRM"]
        MOD_GROWTH["Growth: Marketing, Loyalty, WhatsApp, Marketplace, FlashSales"]
        MOD_ENT["Enterprise: Manufacturing, Branches, Tracking, IOR"]
        MOD_REGIONAL["Regional: Zatca, Maroof, Sadad, NationalAddress"]
        MOD_VERTICAL["Vertical: Restaurant, Salon, Healthcare, Fitness, RealEstate, LMS, Education, Travel, Automotive, Events, Freelancer, Landlord"]
    end

    subgraph "Database Layer"
        DB_MASTER[(tenant_master)]
        DB_R1[(region_mena)]
        DB_R2[(region_europe)]
        DB_R3[(region_south_asia)]
        DB_R4[(region_americas)]
        DB_R5[(region_global)]
    end

    FE_ONBOARD --> MW
    FE_DASH --> MW
    FE_MOD --> MW
    FE_PLATFORM --> MW
    MW --> CTRL --> SVC
    SVC --> MOD_CORE
    SVC --> MOD_GROWTH
    SVC --> DB_MASTER
    SVC --> DB_R1
    SVC --> DB_R2
    SVC --> DB_R3
    SVC --> DB_R4
    SVC --> DB_R5
```

