## 2. Backend Core — Laravel

### Request Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant CORS as DynamicCors
    participant Auth as AuthenticateToken
    participant Tenant as IdentifyTenant
    participant Module as CheckModuleAccess
    participant Ctrl as Controller
    participant Svc as Service
    participant DB as Database

    Client->>CORS: API Request
    CORS->>Auth: Token validation
    Auth->>Tenant: Resolve tenant (header/subdomain)
    Tenant->>Tenant: switchToTenantDatabase()
    Tenant->>Module: Check module subscription
    Module->>Ctrl: Route to controller
    Ctrl->>Svc: Business logic
    Svc->>DB: Query tenant DB
    DB-->>Client: JSON Response
```

### Services (23)

| Category | Service | Purpose |
|----------|---------|---------|
| **Core** | [TenantService](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/TenantService.php#10-169) | Create, provision, cleanup tenants |
| **Core** | [DatabaseManager](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/DatabaseManager.php#9-314) | Create DBs, run migrations, switch connections |
| **Core** | [RegionDatabaseRouter](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/RegionDatabaseRouter.php#16-90) | Route tenants to regional DB servers |
| **Core** | [ModuleService](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/ModuleService.php#12-305) | Subscribe/unsubscribe modules with migrations |
| **Core** | [ModuleMigrationManager](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Services/ModuleMigrationManager.php#9-291) | Run module-specific migrations per tenant |
