### Middleware Stack (13)

| Middleware | Purpose |
|-----------|---------|
| `DynamicCors` | Tenant-aware CORS headers |
| [AuthenticateToken](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Http/Middleware/AuthenticateToken.php#9-86) | JWT/session token validation |
| [IdentifyTenant](file:///e:/Mern%20Stact%20Dev/multi-tenant-mern/multi-tenant-laravel/app/Http/Middleware/IdentifyTenant.php#13-196) | Resolve tenant from header/subdomain, switch DB |
| `IdentifyTenantByUrl` | Resolve tenant from URL pattern |
| `CheckModuleAccess` | Verify tenant has active module subscription |
| `RequireModuleAccess` | Strict module gate |
| `RequirePermission` | RBAC permission check |
| `RequireRole` | Role-based access check |
| `AuthorizeTenantPermission` | Tenant-level permission check |
| `Enforce2FA` | Require 2FA verification |
| `EnforceDatabaseQuota` | Check DB size limits |
| `EnforceAdvancedQuota` | Check advanced feature quotas |
| `LogStaffActivity` | Audit staff actions |

