## 3. Module System — 40 Modules

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "Module Lifecycle"
        REG["Register Module<br/>(modules table)"]
        SUB["Subscribe Tenant<br/>(tenant_modules)"]
        MIG["Run Module Migrations<br/>(on tenant DB)"]
        ACT["Activate & Serve<br/>(CheckModuleAccess)"]
        REN["Renew / Expire<br/>(cron check)"]
    end

    REG --> SUB --> MIG --> ACT --> REN
    REN -->|expired| SUB
```

### Module Categories

| Category | Modules | Status |
|----------|---------|--------|
| **eCommerce Core** | Ecommerce (Products, Orders, Categories, Coupons, Cart, Shipping, Reviews) | ✅ Full |
| **Commerce Growth** | POS, CRM, WhatsApp, Marketplace, FlashSales, Marketing | ✅ Full |
| **Enterprise** | Finance, Inventory, HRM, Manufacturing, Branches, Tracking, IOR | ✅ Full |
| **Saudi Services** | Zatca, Maroof, NationalAddress, Sadad | ✅ Built |
| **Compliance** | Security, Analytics, Pages, SeoManager, Reviews | ✅ Built |
| **Verticals** | Restaurant, Salon, Healthcare, Fitness, RealEstate, LMS, Education, Travel, Automotive, Events, Freelancer, Landlord | 📦 Scaffold |
| **Platform** | AppMarketplace, Contracts, Expenses | 📦 Scaffold |

